<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM18">
<l>ēṟalā lēṟamaṟ ṟillaiyē yemperumā</l>
<l>ṉāṟelām pāyu mavircaṭaiyār vēṟōr</l>
<l>paṭaṅkulavu nākamumiḻ paṇṭamarar cūḻnta</l>
<l>taṭaṅkaṭaṉañ cuṇṭār tamakku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is nothing else to mount than a bull – for him who ate</l>
<l>the poison from the wide ocean surrounded by the immortals,</l>
<l>once spit by another snake gleaming with a hood,</l>
<l>he with shining matted locks from which all the rivers flow.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
